**Example 1: 厨师穿戴识别请求失败**



Input: 

```
tccli tiia DetectChefDress --cli-unfold-argument  \
    --ImageUrl https://123.jpg
```

Output: 
```
{
    "Response": {
        "Error": {
            "Code": "FailedOperation.DownLoadError",
            "Message": "下载失败"
        },
        "RequestId": "a169390a-6ff3-4c42-ad25-a7858c35e576"
    }
}
```
